# Calculator App

This is a calculator app that performs basic arithmetic operations.
It allows users to input an expression and evaluates it.
The app then calculates the result and displays it to the user.

## Features

- Supports basic arithmetic operations (+, -, *, /)
- Handles parentheses for complex expressions
- Provides a simple and intuitive user interface

## Technologies Used

- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Ruby, Sinatra

