## Usage

1. Enter an arithmetic expression in the input field
2. Click the "Evaluate" button or press Enter
3. The result will be displayed below the input field

## Project Structure

- `index.html`: Main HTML file for the frontend
- `server.rb`: Ruby file containing the Sinatra server code
- `tokenize.rb`: Ruby file with the tokenization logic
- `infix_to_postfix.rb`: Ruby file to turn input expression into postfix notation
- `evaluatePostfixExpression.rb`: Ruby file with the expression evaluation logic